00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:06,640
La dedicación a Sahaja Yoga,

184
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:10,920
vuestra pureza acerca de ello,

185
00:12:11,800 --> 00:12:14,320
sin pedir ninguna ganancia,

186
